### Sentences - Search (Editor/Admin)
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/sentences?q=食べる&level=N5&page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Sentences - Get By Id (Editor/Admin)
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/sentences/sentence-001
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Sentences - Create (Editor/Admin)
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/sentences
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
	"text": "昨日、友達と映画を見た。",
	"meaning": "Hom qua toi da xem phim cung ban.",
	"audioUrl": "https://example.com/audio/new-sentence.mp3",
	"level": "N4"
}

###

### Sentences - Update (Editor/Admin)
PATCH {{API_HostAddress}}/api/sentences/sentence-001
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
	"text": "毎朝パンを食べます。",
	"meaning": "Moi sang toi an banh mi.",
	"audioUrl": "https://example.com/audio/s001-updated.mp3",
	"level": "N5"
}

###

### Sentences - Delete (Editor/Admin)
DELETE {{API_HostAddress}}/api/sentences/sentence-001
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

