### Vocabulary - Search (Editor/Admin)
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/vocabulary?q=食べる&level=N5&page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Vocabulary - Search Admin/Editor (with status filter)
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/vocabulary?q=食べる&status=Draft&page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Vocabulary - Get Detail
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/vocabulary/card-001
Accept: application/json

###

### Vocabulary - Create (Editor/Admin)
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/vocabulary
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
	"title": "食べる",
	"summary": "Dong tu an.",
	"level": "N5",
	"tags": ["daily", "verb"],
	"status": "Draft",
	"writing": "食べる",
	"reading": "たべる",
	"pitchPattern": [0, 2],
	"audioUrl": "https://example.com/audio/taberu.mp3",
	"wordType": "Native",
	"meanings": [
		{
			"partOfSpeech": "VerbRu",
			"definitions": ["An", "Tieu thu"]
		}
	],
	"synonyms": ["食す"],
	"antonyms": ["断食する"],
	"relatedPhrases": ["朝ご飯を食べる"]
}

###

### Vocabulary - Update (Editor/Admin)
PATCH {{API_HostAddress}}/api/vocabulary/card-001
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
	"title": "食べる",
	"summary": "Dong tu an (cap nhat).",
	"level": "N5",
	"tags": ["daily", "verb", "basic"],
	"status": "Published",
	"writing": "食べる",
	"reading": "たべる",
	"pitchPattern": [0, 2],
	"audioUrl": "https://example.com/audio/taberu-v2.mp3",
	"wordType": "Native",
	"meanings": [
		{
			"partOfSpeech": "VerbRu",
			"definitions": ["An", "Dung bua"]
		}
	],
	"synonyms": ["食す"],
	"antonyms": ["断食する"],
	"relatedPhrases": ["夕飯を食べる"]
}

###

### Vocabulary - Soft Delete (Editor/Admin)
DELETE {{API_HostAddress}}/api/vocabulary/card-001
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

